_sText:
This is the first map I've made so far, in a soon to be many line of maps (including death match, Bombing, Surf, and hopefully Gun-Game.) It has a couple bugs but there not to bad, just a mis alignment with a couple of things.

From my personal testing this is a good map for a beginner to start practicing and i hope that it is used by at least a few people.

unless something goes wrong ill be making more and better maps in the future. have fun and enjoy. :)
